Farafina kɛŋna Purkinaa Fasoo ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu teyaa kɩgaʊ ŋgbɛyɛ naɖɩyɛ nɛ ɖɩñɔ peeɖe kɛ pɩnaɣ 1978. Farafina weyi payaɣ-ɩ se Mahama Konaté yɔ, ɛmakɩ ɖoŋgaɣ kamaɣ fɛyɩ. Ɛ-wayɩ lɛ Souleymane Sanou wɛŋna nɛ ɛcɔŋna pɛ-ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ ɖɩ-yɔɔ. Souleymane Sanou ɛnɛ, ɛñaɣ pana nɛ ɛcɔɔ ajɛya sakɩyɛ nɛ ɛla maamaacinaa nɛ pɩkɛdɩna ɛyaa. 

Hendu teyaa ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ payaɣ ɖɩɖɩ se Rolling Stones yɔ, ɖɩɩya-yɛ nɛ patɩŋga pɛkpɛndɩ nɛ palɩzɩ hendu teu kɩlɛmɩŋ kanahaʊ nakʊyʊ nɛ payaɣ-kʊ se Continental Drift ,pʊtɔbʊʊ se: ɛjaɖɛ tɛma. Pʊwayɩ lɛ, Jon Hassell  tasɩɩ yaʊ nɛ ɛna-ɩ palɩzɩ kɩlɛmɩŋ kanahaʊ ŋgʊ payaɣ-kʊ  se FLASH OF THE SPIRIT kɛ pɩnaɣ 1987. 

Pɩnaɣ 1988 taa kɛ Farafina cala labʊ amʊʊzɛ kɛ Wɛmble tɛtʊ taa nɛ ɛɖʊ Nelson Mandela hɩɖɛ. Ɖooo ɛzɩ palɩzɩɣ Farafina  kɩgaʊ ŋgbɛyɛ ɖɩnɛ kɛ pɩnzɩ 1980 waa taa yɔ, mba pawɛ pɩtaa yɔ  pa-taa kɔyɔ: Souleymane Sanou, chekere , Soungalo Coulibaly. Sɔnɔ mbʊ yɔ, pɩnaɣ 2012 taa 2012 taa ɛyaa mba pɔsɔza pɔ-yɔɔ yɔ paba yɔ: Fatoumata Dembele, Moussa Sanou, Seydou Dembele, Salif Ouattara, Lamoussa Sanou, Boakary Dembele.
